Available Tools: get_stock_level | check_availability | get_low_stock_items | get_stock_by_location
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "sku": "string", "location_id": "string", "threshold": number }
Response Schema: { "sku": "string", "product_name": "string", "quantity": number, "location": "string", "status": "in_stock|low_stock|out_of_stock" }
---
Question: Determine if the noise-canceling headphones in the Boston hub meet the minimum requirement of 12 units.
Call: { "func_call": "check_availability", "sku": "HP-NC-SLV", "location_id": "BOS-HUB-13", "threshold": 12 }
Response: { "sku": "HP-NC-SLV", "product_name": "Noise Canceling Headphones Silver", "quantity": 9, "location": "BOS-HUB-13", "status": "low_stock" }

